About Get Buzzed DVD



THIS IS NOT PORNOGRAPHY.



Get Buzzed DVD includes shaving instruction for the personal shavers like Cleancut, Body Bare and other personal shavers. The video shows the Body Bare, but can be used to learn the use of any personal shaver. Get Buzzed DVD shows you how to use a personal shaver for the best results. All personal shavers are the same regarding usage. Get Buzzed DVD shows the use of the Body Bare. The Cleancut can follow along with these instructions with the same results. 
Get Buzzed DVD includes instructions for the personal shaver, behind the scenes pics, short movie and cleaning and maintenance instruction.

Get Buzzed is a great DVD to learn how to correctly shave those very intimate sensitive pubic areas. Plus a little extra as well!


Get Buzzed DVD provides:


1)	Personal shaver instructional video

2)	Female shaving instructions

3)	Male shaving instructions

4)	Cleaning and maintenance guidance

5)	Additional Details
